*appstream-glib-0.3.3 (05 Dec 2014)

  05 Dec 2014; Pacho Ramos <pacho@gentoo.org> +appstream-glib-0.3.3.ebuild:
  Version bump

  24 Nov 2014; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> appstream-glib-0.3.2.ebuild:
  [QA] Add missing blocker on colliding versions of dev-util/appdata-tools. Use
  PDEPEND instead of RDEPEND on the metapackage to solve collisions. Fix
  overwritten RDEPEND.

  23 Nov 2014; Gilles Dartiguelongue <eva@gentoo.org>
  appstream-glib-0.3.2.ebuild:
  Do not block apptools-data for now but require dummy package instead.

